LibDIE Changelog
================
This file contains a summary of changes done in each release of the library.

Changes
=======

2019-01-30 Release 0.3
----------------------
  * The build and installation directories can be changed by the user
  * Added the 'uninstall' make target that removes the installed library
  * Added the 'distclean' make target that cleans the build directory
  * Changed the 'clean' make target to remove only files created by make
  * Changed the default installation directory to './local'

2019-01-10 Release 0.2
----------------------
  * Fixed generation of source archives
  * Fixed building on Windows
  * Added a CMAKE module for generating build information
  * Added a new API for querying version information
  * Licensed under GPLv3+